{"tid":1794496,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃色經濟圈] 我地根本拿揑唔到香港既消費模式","createTime":"2019-12-23T06:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T04:11:55.000Z","uid":61886,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"33212735c5b9f4b208c817f0fc98e2c209b5864a","tid":1794496,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"岩岩同朋友去買公司聖誕Party既抽獎禮物<br />\n見到Log on人頭湧湧<br />\n再諗返起尋日睇新聞話好多人出街食飯做節<br />\n就突然知道 <br />\n我地捉唔到黃色經濟圈既重點<br />\n<br />\n1. 節日消費不可避免<br />\n做東食飯、聖誕禮物、新年利是封同揮春、情人節禮物 etc<br />\n依d都算暫時係避免唔到既消費<br />\n與其比人賺<br />\n不如搵黃店做埋佢 比黃店賺 (例如 黃店餐廳做盤菜到會)<br />\n黎緊新年就快到<br />\n唔知有無人會印光復香港利是封<br />\n成本價去設計同印<br />\n有賺既捐d比星火/612<br />\n與其都要買利是封 不如比手足賺<br />\n希望新年 大家都可以用抗爭利是封<br />\n派利是果時順便睇下d藍絲親戚會唔會黑晒面<br />\n<br />\n2. 低物慾消費不等如不消費<br />\n食係最重要既一環<br />\n而家黃店既餐廳仲未夠多<br />\n希望有心有錢有力既可以開多d<br />\n務求每一區都有足夠既選擇比大家<br />\n<br />\n其次係日常用品同消費品<br />\n依一環好需要大家去做大佢<br />\n<br />\n3. 無必要格硬降低物慾<br />\n但要將消費放o係黃店身上<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"6f4b1ceeaaf111a109fc2f16da4e89c6152b5026","tid":1794496,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgwZ4tD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgwZ4tD.jpg&h=52b479a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGepv8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGepv8D.jpg&h=265d7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgLfAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgLfAm.jpg&h=e2a8e121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"541f36ecf733303791c651da26620188eb339647","tid":1794496,"uid":203397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8tE5W9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8tE5W9.jpg&h=9dd1eb2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFreelancer抗爭講座：<br />\n音樂導師、電影工作者、傳媒人分享～<br />\n<br />\n三罷吹鷄，各行各業打工仔紛紛成立工會，為長遠抗爭做準備，對於本來勞工保障就較少的Freelancer而言，他們的抗爭又是怎樣呢？我們邀請了三個範疇的Freelancers跟大家分享他們的工運抗爭，包括對工會、組織模式、罷工等想法。希望大家對各行業有更深入了解，並且為強而有力的大罷工做更好準備。<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年12月27日（周五）<br />\n時間：晚上7時30分<br />\n地點：［土家］土瓜灣，鴻福街16號/地舖<br />\n主辦：勞工組<br />\n嘉賓：<br />\n任俠（香港編劇權益聯盟成員）<br />\n小菁（傳媒工作者/勞工組成員）<br />\nGloria（香港音樂人工會主席）<br />\n查詢/聯絡：telegram @Kakaxop<br />\n<br />\n=== === === ===<br />\n勞工組和你追頻道：telegram @workercom<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1363794490446915/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1076113639215003%2Fposts%2F1363794490446915%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwWmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=5380d512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1363794490446915/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"5fce33ee1a8635b76bbcff88a49020350c1d77e8","tid":1794496,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T07:05:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"be45eabbca0321e84f49493a15fa1e6dd2ff78b4","tid":1794496,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"72f74c1cb25b495c458e643c65ff79ddbcfb21a3","tid":1794496,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"39c6c87f05180ea508c8c80cbc6642b0335b1f47","tid":1794496,"uid":186181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T07:11:36.000Z","msg":"食野都還好<br />\n買野既舖頭真係少選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095dd42c10b37c728a52cbca3b4ae2a881277017","tid":1794496,"uid":35946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"提供alternative 俾消費嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0a4a1bb15a82eb6e14b86ae4bbf237b2d12cf8","tid":1794496,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2